text: Fabio Badraun (born 4 October 1987) is a Swiss bobsledder. He competed in the four-man event at the 2018 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss male bobsledders Category:Olympic bobsledders of Switzerland Category:Bobsledders at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
